lUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex%20Navyman%20Wanted%20For%20Murder%20Faked%20Death%2C%20Luck%20Ran%20Out%2020%20Years%20Later%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Navy%20employee%2C%20who%20had%20been%20living%20under%20a%20false%20identity%20after%20faking%20his%20death%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20choking%20a%20man%20to%20death%20and%20setting%20two%20others%20on%20fire%20nearly%2020%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBalesh%20Kumar%2C%20now%2060%2C%20was%20arrested%20after%20Delhi%20Police%20received%20information%20that%20a%20man%20wanted%20for%20a%202004%20murder%20in%20Delhi's%20Bawana%20locality%20was%20living%20at%20Najafgarh%2C%20nearly%2030%20km%20away.%20Kumar%20had%20changed%20his%20name%20to%20Aman%20Singh%20and%20had%20been%20working%20as%20a%20property%20dealer%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20crime%20branch%20senior%20officer%20Ravinder%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20police%20arrested%20Kumar%20following%20an%20investigation%20that%20confirmed%20their%20suspicions%2C%20chilling%20details%20came%20to%20the%20fore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Haryana%2C%20Kumar%20had%20studied%20till%20Class%208.%20He%20joined%20the%20Navy%20in%201981%20and%20retired%20in%201996.%20After%20that%2C%20he%20started%20a%20transport%20business%20and%20lived%20in%20Delhi's%20Uttam%20Nagar%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumar%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20and%20his%20brother%20Sunder%20Lal%20had%20choked%20a%20person%20named%20Rajesh%20at%20Delhi's%20Samaypur%20Badli%20in%202004.%20He%20has%20said%20the%20three%20were%20drinking%20when%20an%20altercation%20broke%20out%20over%20an%20alleged%20extramarital%20affair%20between%20Kumar%20and%20Rajesh's%20wife.%20The%20argument%20turned%20to%20a%20scuffle%2C%20and%20Kumar%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20both%20intoxicated%2C%20choked%20Rajesh%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumar%20then%20plotted%20an%20escape%20plan.%20He%20hired%20two%20labourers%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Manoj%20and%20Mukesh%2C%20from%20Delhi's%20Samaypur%20Badli%2C%20and%20promised%20them%20work.%20The%20three%20then%20left%20for%20Rajasthan%20in%20a%20truck%20belonging%20to%20Kumar's%20brother.%20At%20Jodhpur%2C%20Kumar%20allegedly%20set%20the%20truck%20on%20fire%2C%20with%20the%20labourers%20inside.%20He%20then%20left%20his%20documents%20inside.%20When%20police%20reached%20the%20spot%2C%20one%20of%20the%20bodies%20was%20identified%20as%20that%20of%20Kumar's.%20The%20other%20body%20was%20not%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rajesh's%20murder%20case%20came%20up%20in%20court%2C%20police%20said%20Sunder%20Lal%20had%20been%20arrested%20and%20Kumar%20was%20dead%20in%20the%20truck%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumar's%20wife%20got%20his%20pension%20benefits%20and%20life%20insurance%20amount.%20The%20insurance%20for%20the%20truck%20was%20also%20routed%20to%20his%20wife.%20His%20past%20identity%20and%20crimes%20had%20been%20well%20covered%20up%2C%20till%20luck%20ran%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20have%20now%20asked%20their%20Jodhpur%20counterparts%20to%20reopen%20the%20truck%20fire%20case%20following%20the%20new%20revelations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697602320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F65hfl0rg_ex-navy-man_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fex-navyman-wanted-for-murder-faked-death-luck-ran-out-20-years-later-4491253%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20Navy%20employee%2C%20who%20had%20been%20living%20under%20a%20false%20identity%20after%20faking%20his%20death%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20choking%20a%20man%20to%20death%20and%20setting%20two%20others%20on%20fire%20nearly%2020%20years%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fex-navyman-wanted-for-murder-faked-death-luck-ran-out-20-years-later-4491253%