%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20memoir%2C%20Timberlake%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20wasn't%20happy%20about%20the%20pregnancy.%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%20we%20weren't%20ready%20to%20have%20a%20baby%20in%20our%20lives%2C%20that%20we%20were%20way%20too%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%3A%20%26quot%3BTo%20this%20day%2C%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20agonizing%20things%20I%20have%20ever%20experienced%20in%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Timberlake%2C%20now%2042%20and%20married%20to%20actor%20Jessica%20Biel%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20request%20for%20comment.%20Following%20the%20split%20with%20Timberlake%2C%20Spears%20had%20two%20sons%20-%20Sean%20and%20Jayden%20-%20with%20her%20second%20husband%20Kevin%20Federline.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20after%20suffering%20a%20highly%20public%20breakdown%2C%20Spears%20was%20placed%20under%20a%20unique%20legal%20guardianship%20largely%20governed%20by%20her%20father%2C%20Jamie.%20During%20a%20court%20appearance%20in%202021%2C%20she%20told%20a%20judge%20that%20the%20conservatorship%20was%20preventing%20her%20from%20removing%20a%20contraceptive%20IUD%20-%20despite%20her%20wanting%20to%20get%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conservatorship%20stripped%20me%20of%20my%20womanhood%2C%20made%20me%20into%20a%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Spears%2C%20in%20another%20excerpt.%20She%20also%20writes%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20back%20now%20on%20my%20father%20and%20his%20associates%20having%20control%20over%20my%20body%20and%20my%20money%20for%20that%20long%20and%20it%20makes%20me%20feel%20sick.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20guardianship%20was%20scrapped%20in%20November%202021.%20Spears%20became%20pregnant%20in%202022%2C%20but%20later%20announced%20she%20had%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20her%20third%20husband%2C%20Sam%20Asghari%2C%20said%20the%20pair%20were%20filing%20for%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3