%20Strikes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20wartime%20trip%20to%20Israel%20and%20Jordan%20faltered%20before%20it%20got%20off%20the%20ground%20Tuesday%2C%20after%20the%20Amman%20leg%20was%20canceled%20following%20a%20strike%20on%20a%20Gaza%20hospital%20that%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20people.%3Cbr%3E%20The%20trip%20was%20always%20set%20to%20be%20the%20riskiest%20of%20Biden's%20presidency%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20juggle%20support%20for%20Israel%20after%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks%20with%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20a%20humanitarian%20disaster%20in%20Gaza%20and%20to%20avert%20a%20wider%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20regional%20balancing%20act%20came%20undone%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20his%20visit%20with%20news%20of%20the%20hospital%20explosion%20--%20for%20which%20Hamas%20blamed%20Israeli%20strikes%2C%20while%20Israel%20said%20it%20was%20caused%20by%20a%20rocket%20misfired%20by%20militants%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Biden%2C%2080%2C%20climbed%20the%20steps%20of%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20Jordan%20announced%20that%20a%20planned%20four-way%20summit%20with%20Palestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%2C%20Jordanian%20King%20Abdullah%20II%20and%20Egypt's%20president%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20was%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20held%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20the%20decision%20to%20stop%20the%20war%20and%20put%20an%20end%20to%20these%20massacres%20has%20been%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Foreign%20Minister%20Ayman%20Safadi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20later%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Boutraged%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bexplosion%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20had%20told%20his%20national%20security%20team%20to%20get%20more%20information%20on%20what%20had%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Solidarity'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20however%20told%20reporters%20aboard%20the%20presidential%20plane%20said%20that%20the%20Israelis%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20very%20strongly%20this%20was%20not%20caused%20by%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bmutual%20decision%26quot%3B%20to%20cancel%20the%20Jordan%20trip%20after%20Abbas%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20return%20home%20for%20three%20days%20of%20mourning%2C%20and%20that%20Biden%20would%20speak%20to%20him%20and%20Sisi%20by%20phone%20on%20the%20plane%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20Biden%20will%20now%20be%20flying%20into%20an%20even%20more%20volatile%20situation%20than%20before%2C%20with%20the%20hospital%20strike%20sparking%20anger%20across%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurious%20protesters%20tried%20to%20storm%20the%20Israeli%20embassy%20in%20Amman%20where%20Biden%20was%20due%20to%20meet%20the%20other%20leaders%2C%20while%20in%20Tehran%20hundreds%20rallied%20outside%20the%20French%20and%20British%20embassies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELebanon's%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bday%20of%20rage%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20strike%20to%20coincide%20with%20Biden's%20arrival%2C%20fueling%20fears%20of%20the%20very%20escalation%20by%20Tehran%20and%20its%20allies%20that%20Biden's%20visit%20is%20supposed%20to%20warn%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20Biden%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20to%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%26quot%3B%20after%20Hamas%20burst%20through%20its%20heavily%20fortified%20Gaza%20border%2C%20shooting%2C%20stabbing%20and%20burning%20to%20death%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20would%20hold%20talks%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20and%20his%20war%20cabinet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20meeting%20the%20families%20of%20some%20of%20those%20killed%20and%20missing%20in%20the%20attacks%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKirby%20insisted%20however%20that%20Biden%20would%20ask%20Netanyahu%20%26quot%3Btough%20questions%26quot%3B%20about%20his%20plans%20for%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Risks'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NSC%20spokesman%20added%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Boptimistic%26quot%3B%20that%20aid%20would%20start%20to%20get%20through%20to%20stricken%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Democratic%20president%20deliberated%20carefully%20before%20accepting%20the%20invitation%20to%20visit%20from%20right-winger%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20ordered%20preparations%20for%20what%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20bloody%20ground%20offensive%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20always%20a%20risk%20that%20by%20coming%20to%20Israel%20Biden%20would%20find%20himself%20too%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20Israeli%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20leveled%20huge%20swaths%20and%20killed%20more%20than%203%2C000%20people%2C%20and%20the%20siege%20of%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20hospital%20attack%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btrip%20fraught%20with%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnger%20over%20the%20hospital%20strike%20could%20meanwhile%20undermine%20the%20wider%20purpose%20of%20Biden's%20visit%20as%20he%20tries%20to%20prevent%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20engulfing%20the%20wider%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20warned%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah%20not%20to%20get%20involved%20and%20has%20dispatched%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20to%20deter%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKirby%20again%20said%20there%20were%20no%20plans%20to%20put%20US%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20but%20added%20that%20the%20American%20military%20assets%20were%20in%20place%20to%20%26quot%3Bdemonstrate%20a%20sincere%20capability%20of%20protecting%20and%20defending%26quot%3B%20US%20national%20security%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publis