New%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20al-Ahli%20Baptist%20hospital%20which%20was%20bombed%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20is%20one%20of%2022%20hospitals%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20which%20were%20ordered%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20to%20evacuate%20their%20patients%20and%20staff%20within%2024%20hours%20or%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20evacuation%20order%20was%20issued%20late%20on%20October%2012%2C%20and%20drew%20swift%20condemnation%20from%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20and%20other%20UN%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20United%20Nation%E2%80%99s%20agency%20responsible%20for%20public%20health%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20strongly%20condemns%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20orders%20for%20the%20evacuation%20of%2022%20hospitals%20treating%20more%20than%202000%20inpatients%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20WHO%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20forced%20evacuation%20of%20patients%20and%20health%20workers%20will%20further%20worsen%20the%20current%20humanitarian%20and%20public%20health%20catastrophe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CForcing%20more%20than%202000%20patients%20to%20relocate%20to%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20where%20health%20facilities%20are%20already%20running%20at%20maximum%20capacity%20and%20unable%20to%20absorb%20a%20dramatic%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20patients%2C%20could%20be%20tantamount%20to%20a%20death%20sentence%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20statement%20also%20noted%20that%20hospital%20compounds%20in%20Gaza%20had%20emerged%20as%20spaces%20where%20displaced%20Gazans%20had%20gathered%20in%20large%20numbers%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20hospitals%20would%20not%20be%20attacked%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20displaced%20people%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20are%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20open%20spaces%20in%20or%20around%20hospitals%2C%20treating%20them%20as%20havens%20from%20violence%20as%20well%20as%20to%20protect%20the%20facilities%20from%20potential%20attacks.%20Their%20lives%2C%20too%2C%20are%20at%20risk%20when%20health%20facilities%20are%20bombed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20targeting%20of%20hospitals%20is%20a%20war%20crime%20under%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20the%20WHO%20issued%20this%20statement%2C%20which%20also%20called%20on%20Israel%20to%20rescind%20its%20evacuation%20order%2C%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20was%20hit%20by%20Israeli%20rocket%20fire%2C%20injuring%20four%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.archbishopofcanterbury.org%2Fnews%2Fnews-and-statements%2Fgaza-hospitals-are-facing-catastrophe-says-archbishop-canterbury%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%20by%20the%20Archbishop%20of%20Canterbury%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Anglican%20church%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHospitals%20and%20patients%20in%20Gaza%20are%20in%20grave%20danger.%20The%20seriously%20ill%20and%20injured%20patients%20at%20the%20Anglican-run%20Ahli%20Hospital%20%E2%80%93%20and%20other%20healthcare%20facilities%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20cannot%20be%20safely%20evacuated.%20They%20are%20running%20low%20on%20medical%20supplies.%20They%20are%20facing%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Ahli%20Hospital%20was%20hit%20by%20Israeli%20rocket%20fire%20last%20night%2C%20with%20four%20staff%20injured%20in%20the%20blast.%20Other%20hospitals%20have%20also%20been%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20appeal%20for%20the%20evacuation%20order%20on%20hospitals%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20to%20be%20reversed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20for%20health%20facilities%2C%20health%20workers%2C%20patients%20and%20civilians%20to%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20evil%20and%20barbaric%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israelis%20by%20Hamas%20were%20a%20blasphemous%20outrage.%20But%20the%20civilians%20of%20Gaza%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20crimes%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPlease%20continue%20to%20pray%20for%20all%20innocent%20people%2C%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%2C%20who%20are%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20terrible%20violence%20in%20the%20Holy%20Land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98War%20crime%20is%20a%20specific%20term.%20The%20WHO%20can%E2%80%99t%20determine%20that%E2%80%99%3A%20WHO%20representative%20at%20presser%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20issuing%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20UN%20health%20body%20in%20a%20hurriedly%20convened%20presser%20said%20it%20was%20still%20trying%20to%20ascertain%20the%20full%20scale%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20human%20life%20and%20other%20resources%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERichard%20Peeperkorn%2C%20WHO%20Representative%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98occupied%20Palestinian%20territory%20%5Bthis%20is%20WHO%20nomenclature%5D%2C%20said%20he%20had%20seen%20media%20reports%20saying%20the%20number%20of%20dead%20in%20the%20attack%20could%20range%20from%20200-800.%20%E2%80%9CI%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20speculate%20%5Bthe%20number%20of%20dead%5D%20but%20it%20will%20be%20verified%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20did%20not%20say%20how%20many%20patients%20were%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20the%20hospital%20at%20the%20time%20of%20attack%20but%20all%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20all%20hospitals%20are%20overwhelmed%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20WHO%20officials%20did%20say%20in%20the%20presser%20that%20%E2%80%98thousands%20and%20thousands%E2%80%99%20of%20internally%20displaced%20people%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20the%20hospitals%20since%20they%20considered%20it%20a%20place%20that%20was%20immune%20to%20any%20military%20attack.%20And%2C%20al-Alhi%20hospital%20was%20no%20exception%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20NGO%20MSF%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMSF%2Fstatus%2F1714363238240973125%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20out%20a%20tweet%20by%20one%20of%20its%20doctors%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20following%20the%20bombing%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20operating%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20explosion%2C%20and%20the%20ceiling%20fell%20on%20the%20operating%20room.%20This%20is%20a%20massacre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Ghassan%20Abu%20Sittah%2C%20MSF%20doctor%20in%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20non-profit%20organisations%20working%20in%20healthcare%20have%20condemned%20the%20attack.%20US-based%20%E2%80%98Physicians%20for%20Human%20Rights%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20also%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%2C%20called%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98deadliest%20attack%20on%20healthcare%20across%20any%20conflict%20in%20the%20world%20in%20recent%20years%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20call%20for%20an%20impartial%2C%20independent%2C%20international%20investigation%20into%20the%20Al-Ahli%20al-Arabi%20Hospital%20strike.%20The%20perpetrators%20must%20be%20held%20to%20account%20for%20this%20serious%20violation%20of%20international%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMedicines%20Sans%20Frontiers%20(MSF)%20said%20it%20was%20horrified%20by%20the%20attack.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20operating%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20explosion%2C%20and%20the%20ceiling%20fell%20on%20the%20operating%20room.%20This%20is%20a%20massacre%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Ghassan%20Abu%20Sittah%2C%20an%20MSF%20doctor%20in%20Gaza%2C%20has%20been%20quoted%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20bloodshed%20must%20stop.%20Enough%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20attack%20%E2%80%98totally%20unacceptable%E2%80%99%2C%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%2C%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20said%2C%20once%20again%2C%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20section%20of%20people%20were%20targeted.%20He%20demanded%20the%20guilty%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20and%20gave%20a%20call%20to%20%E2%80%98all%20States%20with%20influence%E2%80%99%20to%20do%20%E2%80%98everything%20in%20their%20power%20to%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20this%20horrendous%20situation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20bombing%2C%20doctors%20from%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20amidst%20the%20bodies%20of%20some%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20victims%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20bombing%20on%20October%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20current%20conflict%20started%2C%203%2C000%20people%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20Palestine%2C%20according%20to%20the%20WHO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20said%20before%20the%20attack%20on%20al-Ahli%20hospital%2C%20there%20had%20been%20115%20attacks%20on%20%E2%80%98health%E2%80%99%20in%20Palestine%20with%2051%20of%20them%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20rest%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20As%20many%20as%2015%20healthcare%20workers%20had%20been%20killed%20on%20the%20line%20of%20duty%20while%2027%20others%20were%20injured.%20As%20many%20as%2024%20health%20facilities%20were%20affected%20and%20damaged%20in%20Gaza%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20refused%20to%20say%20if%20they%20had%20any%20information%20whether%20the%20attack%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20or%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20information%20that%20they%20could%20have%20gathered%20from%20their%20team%20on%20the%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20for%20criminal%20investigation%20to%20find%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mike%20Ryan%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Health%20Emergencies%20Programme.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20WHO%20can%E2%80%99t%20determine%20the%20origin%20or%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20weapon.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20condemn%20the%20attack%20of%20this%20ferocity..%20of%20this%20scale%20of%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20agency%20experts%20also%20did%20not%20say%20whether%20they%20would%20like%20to%20classify%20the%20attack%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98war%20crime%E2%80%99%2C%20while%20replying%20to%20a%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20query%2C%20even%20though%20they%20condemned%20it%20very%20strongly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWar%20crime%20is%20a%20specific%20term.%20The%20WHO%20can%E2%80%99t%20determine%20that%E2%80%A6the%20causation%20or%20attribution%20is%20a%20vast%20call%20for%20the%20WHO%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ryan%20said%2C%20while%20adding%20that%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20calls%20for%20protection%20of%20healthcare%20and%20healthcare%20workers.%20And%2C%20any%20such%20attack%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20laws%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20expressed%20%E2%80%98frustration%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20truckloads%20of%20essential%20supplies%2C%20including%20medicine%2C%20equipment%2C%20food%20and%20other%20such%20materials%20were%20lying%20idle%20at%20Egypt%E2%80%99s%20border%20while%20the%20people%20in%20Gaza%20are%20suffering%20badly%20due%20to%20scarcity%20of%20these%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20to%20clarify%20if%20the%20problem%20was%20from%20Israeli%20side%20or%20Egyptian%2C%20Richard%20Brennan%2C%20Regional%20Emergency%20Director%20of%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Eastern%20Mediterranean%20Regional%20Office%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Rafah%20crossing%20remains%20closed%20at%20this%20stage%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20aid%20that%20has%20built%20up%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20side%E2%80%A6We%E2%80%99re%20ready%20to%20go%20as%20soon%20as%20there%20is%20an%20opening.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERyan%20added%20it%20was%20not%20just%20about%20the%20Rafah%20crossing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20far%20side%20of%20that%20crossing.%20Because%20delivering%20aid%20to%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20crossing%20is%20not%20good%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3411.0089965298594!2d34.256848775600666!3d31.248174274339785!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14fd93842067f5cd%253A0x330d09c6cad7ca73!2sRafah%2520Crossing!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1697598388592!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20are%20scattered%20all%20over%20Gaza.%20The%20hospitals%20are%20scattered%20all%20over%20Gaza.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20safe%20access%20to%20those%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ryan%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20why%20the%20supplies%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20transported%20further%20from%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20into%20Gaza%2C%20Brennan%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20dynamics%20going%20on.%20We%20understand%20that.%20We%20know%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20diplomacy%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20senior%20UN%20officials%20were%20arriving%20at%20Egypt%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Cario%20that%20night%20and%20the%20next%20day%20he%20hoped%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20negotiate%20with%20all%20the%20relevant%20parties%20to%20get%20the%20opening%20going%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20of%20healthcare%20centres%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20of%20healthcare%20centres%2C%20Peeperkorn%20said%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20primary%20health%20centres%20were%20not%20functioning%20in%20Palestine.%20As%20far%20as%20hospitals%20are%20concerned%2C%2030%20out%20of%2034%20were%20functioning%20but%20with%20fast-dwindling%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20medicines%20required%20not%20just%20for%20surgeries%20and%20trauma%20were%20nearly%20exhausted%20but%20even%20basic%20things%20such%20as%20cleaning%20materials%20for%20hospital%20wards.%20Therefore%2C%20hospitals%20are%20now%20reporting%20cases%20of%20infections%20arising%20out%20of%20unhygienic%20conditions%20in%20the%20wards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20patients%20who%20suffer%20from%20diseases%20such%20as%20cardiovascular%2C%20oncology%20and%20other%20such%20ailments%20are%20not%20able%20to%20find%20medicines%20anymore.%20It%20had%20become%20difficult%20for%20hospitals%20even%20to%20cater%20to%20pregnant%20women.%20The%20blood%20banks%20are%20also%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20dried%20up%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorse%2C%20the%20hospitals%20may%20run%20out%20of%20fuel%20in%20a%20day%20or%20so%2C%20Peepkorn%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%2C%20the%20WHO%20officials%20also%20feared%20outbreak%20of%20communicable%20diseases.%20Lack%20of%20drinking%20water%20and%20sanitation%20services%20would%20only%20exacerbate%20the%20health%20issues%20of%20the%20people%20living%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Peepkorn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20officials%20reversal%20of%20evacuation%20order%20given%20by%20Israel.%20Even%20in%20most%20advanced%20countries%2C%20evacuation%20of%20patients%20admitted%20with%20serious%20injuries%20was%20impossible%2C%20Ryan%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20doing%20it%20in%20a%20conflict-ridden%20situation%20in%20which%20incessant%20attacks%20and%20bombings%20were%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20WHO%20had%20called%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20evacuation%20order%20a%20death%20sentence%20for%20patients%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20the%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERyan%20also%20said%20the%20WHO%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20Israel%20and%20had%20offered%20medical%20assistance.%20But%20since%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20medical%20system%20was%20highly%20advanced%2C%20the%20country%20did%20not%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20take%20any%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%2C%20first%20published%20at%205.38%20am%20on%20October%2018%2C%202023%2C%20was%20updated%20and%20republished%20at%208%20am%20on%20the%20same%20day%20with%20details%20on%20the%20WHO%20presser.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697596232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18045004%2Fal-ahli-pc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdays-before-catastrophic-bombing-of-gaza-hospital-israel-had-fired-rocket-ordered-its-evacuation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20targeting%20of%20hospitals%20is%20a%20war%20crime%20under%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdays-before-catastrophic-bombing-of-gaza-hospital-israel-had-fired-rocket-ordered-its-evacuation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%20Polls%3A%20Ascendant%20Congress%20Plans%20to%20Take%20the%20Fight%20To%20Disgruntled%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17180205%2Fcollage.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESetting%20the%20agenda%20for%20the%202023%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20October%2017%2C%20released%20a%20manifesto%20promising%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20state%20if%20voted%20to%20power%20along%20with%20the%20resolve%20to%20provide%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20health%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20accident%20insurance%20for%20all%20and%20buy%20cow%20dung%20from%20farmers%20at%20Rs%202%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reservation%20limit%20for%20backward%20castes%20would%20be%20based%20on%20the%20numbers%20revealed%20in%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20party%20said%20in%20its%20%3Cem%3Evachan%20patra%3C%2Fem%3E%20released%20in%20Bhopal%20by%20senior%20leaders%20led%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20agrarian%20community%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20its%20government%20would%20purchase%20paddy%20from%20farmers%20at%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20quintal%20and%20wheat%20at%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20increasing%20it%20to%20Rs%2C%203%2C000%20per%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENath%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20CM%20face%20in%20the%20state%2C%20said%20the%20party%20would%20make%20efforts%20to%20get%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20its%20own%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20team.%20The%20more%20than%201%2C200%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20its%20vachan%20patra%20touched%2059%20major%20themes%20and%20229%20pointers.%20This%20included%20the%20promise%20to%20provide%20the%20educated%20unemployed%20youth%20with%20Rs%2015%2C00-3%2C000%20per%20month%20and%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20every%20woman%20per%20month%20under%20the%20Nari%20Samman%20Yojana%20and%20Rs%201.01%20support%20sum%20for%20the%20marriage%20of%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20manifesto%20reiterated%20some%20of%20the%20social%20welfare%20promises%20already%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20voters%20in%20its%20public%20rallies%20following%20its%20thumping%20success%20in%20Karnataka%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Under%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20LPG%20cylinders%20would%20cost%20Rs%20500%20and%20not%20Rs%201%2C000%3B%20electricity%20bills%20for%20100%20units%20of%20power%20would%20be%20waived%20off%2C%20while%20it%20would%20be%20halved%20for%20200%20units%3B%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20could%20be%20implemented%20and%20farm%20loans%20would%20be%20waived%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20its%2018%20years%20in%20power%2C%20the%20BJP%20ruined%20every%20institution%20and%20system.%20MP%E2%80%99s%20economy%20was%20ruined.%20The%20youth%20are%20unemployed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680509%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKamal%20Nath%2C%20Digvijay%20Singh%20and%20others%20release%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20October%2017.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40OfficeofKNath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20rival%20and%20present%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20was%20quick%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20promises%2C%20dismissing%20them%20as%20lies.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Emaha%20jhooth%20patra%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Five%20years%20ago%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20made%20900%20promises%20but%20did%20not%20implement%20even%20nine%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20a%20month%20left%20for%20voting%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20election%2C%20Chouhan%20is%20at%20an%20unfamiliar%20crossroads.%20Though%20he%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20the%20state%20since%202005%2C%20a%20remarkable%20feat%20by%20all%20means%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fshivraj-chouhan-position-bommai-defeat-bjp-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3Euncertainty%20looms%20large%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20his%20own%20political%20future.%20Will%20Chouhan%20return%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20CM%20even%20if%20the%20party%20wins%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20question%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20political%20observers%2C%20as%20the%20central%20Indian%20state%20with%20230%20assembly%20seats%20heads%20to%20another%20tight%20battle%20%E2%80%93%20just%20like%20the%20one%20it%20witnessed%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChouhan%20lost%20power%20in%20that%20election%20and%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%20a%20little%20over%20a%20year%20before%20returning%20as%20CM%20after%20almost%20two%20dozen%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20led%20by%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20defected%20and%20toppled%20the%20Kamal%20Nath-led%20government.%20In%202023%2C%20Chouhan%2C%20once%20seen%20as%20a%20possible%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20fighting%20two%20battles%3A%20one%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20keep%20the%20Congress%20out%20and%20the%20second%2C%20a%20lone%20one%2C%20for%20his%20own%20political%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20finally%20announced%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20its%20fourth%20list%20of%20candidates%20last%20week%2C%20after%20agonising%20speculation%20over%20the%20possibility%20of%20him%20being%20dropped%2C%20the%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20officially%20declare%20him%20as%20the%20CM%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20challenged%20by%20an%20ascendant%20and%20confident%20Congress%2C%20led%20by%20its%20state%20president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20has%20been%20leading%20from%20the%20front%20in%20anchoring%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20strategy%2C%20incorporating%20rebels%20from%20the%20saffron%20camp%20and%20responding%20to%20his%20opponents%20with%20wit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20made%20a%20remarkable%20jump%20from%2050-odd%20seats%20in%202013%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20MP%20assembly.%20The%20party%20won%20114%20seats%20but%20fell%20just%20short%20of%20the%20golden%20halfway%20mark%20by%20just%20two%20seats.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tally%20dropped%20to%20109%2C%20even%20though%20the%20saffron%20party%20had%20a%20marginally%20higher%20vote%20count%20and%20vote%20percentage.%20With%20the%20support%20of%20two%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MLAs%2C%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLA%20and%20four%20independent%20winners%2C%20the%20Congress%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20CM.%20Though%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20wrest%20back%20control%20of%20the%20state%20after%20the%20rebellion%20by%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20its%20government%20headed%20by%20Chouhan%20post-2020%20was%20already%20running%20against%20popular%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChouhan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20position%20only%20seem%20to%20have%20become%20weaker%20since%20then%2C%20as%20the%20continuous%20rebellions%20and%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20put%20faith%20in%20Chouhan%20as%20its%20face%2C%20indicate.%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20add%20a%20darker%20shade%20of%20Hindutva%20to%20his%20well-cultivated%20image%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmama%E2%80%9D%20through%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkhargone-ram-navami-violence-bulldozer%5C%22%3Ebulldozers%20to%20demolish%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20targets%20and%20shriller%20rhetoric%20have%20done%20little%20to%20redeem%20his%20position.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20control%20the%20damage%20by%20announcing%20new%20schemes%20and%20measures%20like%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20and%2035%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20jobs%2C%20even%20this%20has%20not%20been%20enough%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20declare%20him%20as%20their%20official%20CM%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-experimental-strategy-union-ministers-mps-assembly-elections-modi%5C%22%3Efielding%3C%2Fa%3E%20three%20Union%20ministers%2C%20four%20MPs%20and%20a%20national%20general%20secretary%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20them%20possible%20contenders%20for%20the%20top%20post%20%E2%80%93%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20position%20increasingly%20looks%20precarious.%20At%20a%20recent%20rally%2C%20Chouhan%20made%20an%20emotional%20appeal%20to%20the%20voters.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20run%20the%20government.%20I%20run%20a%20family.%20You%20will%20not%20find%20a%20brother%20like%20this.%20You%20will%20miss%20me%20when%20I%20am%20gone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EK.K.%20Mishra%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20media%20department%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20MP%2C%20is%20dismissive%20of%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20%E2%80%9CShivraj%20Singh%3Cem%3Eji%20thay%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Kamal%20Nath%3Cem%3Eji%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Shivraj%20Singh%20is%20past.%20Kamal%20Nath%20is%20the%20present%20and%20the%20future)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CChouhan%20has%20not%20been%20declared%20the%20CM%20candidate%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20consider%20him%20a%20face%2C%20so%20why%20shall%20we%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChouhan%E2%80%99s%20future%20is%20not%20the%20only%20issue%20dominating%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20this%20season.%20The%20election%20result%20would%20also%20be%20a%20commentary%20on%20Union%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20who%20had%20rebelled%20against%20the%20Congress%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20and%20help%20the%20latter%20form%20the%20government.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20several%20Scindia%20loyalists%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharaj-doesnt-have-power-in-the-bjp-scindias-clout-wanes-as-loyalists-return-to-congress%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20many%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20legislators%20past%20and%20present%20have%20also%20shifted%20ranks%20to%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20the%20disquiet%20caused%20in%20the%20saffron%20camp%20by%20the%20entry%20of%20Scindia%20loyalists%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20northern%20belts%20of%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490703%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJyotiraditya%20Scindia.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40JM_Scindia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20fighting%20this%20election%20with%20a%20multi-pronged%20approach%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20its%20star%20campaigner%2C%20as%20expected.%20The%20party%20is%20trying%20to%20sell%20the%20idea%20that%20it%20has%20rid%20the%20state%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98BIMARU%E2%80%99%20image%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20recently%20launched%20a%20report%20card%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20the%20state%20from%202003%20to%202023%20under%20the%20Gareeb%20Kalyan%20Mahaabhiyan.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20written%20off%2C%20the%20state%20is%20now%20in%20the%20list%20of%20the%20prosperous%20and%20happy%20states%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah%2C%20listing%20achievements%20in%20water%20supply%2C%20electricity%2C%20education%2C%20roads%2C%20economy%2C%20irrigation%2C%20law%20and%20order%2C%20health%20and%20other%20indices.%20He%20said%20that%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20MP%20in%202003%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20per%20capita%20income%20had%20increased%20from%20Rs%2011%2C700%20to%20Rs%201.40%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20election%20is%20to%20completely%20free%20people%20from%20poverty%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congresss-obc-politics-in-madhya-pradesh-is-to-shivraj-singh-chauhans-benefit%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20High%20Command%20Is%20Alarmed%20by%20MP%20CM%20Shivraj%20Blowing%20Hot%20and%20Cold%20on%20His%20Future%20Plans%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20on%20the%20front%20foot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%20has%20taken%20the%20BJP%20and%20Chouhan%20head-on.%20He%20has%20released%20an%20%3Cem%3Eaarop%20patra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chargesheet)%20of%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20scams%20under%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20%E2%80%93%20a%20document%20titled%20%E2%80%9CGhotala%20hi%20Ghotala%E2%80%94Ghotala%20seth%2C%2050%25%20commission%20rate.%E2%80%9D%20In%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20youth%20on%20October%2011%2C%20Nath%20said%20that%20in%20the%2018%20years%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%2C%20it%20pushed%20its%20level%20of%20education%20and%20skills%20to%20new%20lows%2C%20leading%20to%20unemployment.%20%E2%80%9CToday%20MP%20identifies%20as%20a%20state%20with%20recruitment%20scams%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nath.%20Apart%20from%20questioning%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20record%20on%20corruption%2C%20jobs%2C%20inflation%20and%20law%20and%20order%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20its%20own%20slew%20of%20welfare%20promises%2C%20including%20waiving%20off%20farmer%20debt%2C%20100%20units%20of%20free%20power%2C%20Rs%201%2C500%20monthly%20stipend%20for%20women%20and%20free%20education%20till%20Class%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECaste%20has%20also%20taken%20centre-stage%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20this%20election.%20The%20party%20has%20emphatically%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-bihar-cong-govt-in-rajasthan-to-conduct-caste-survey-makes-it-main-agenda-in-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3Ecaste%20survey%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20one%20conducted%20in%20Bihar%2C%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%20This%2C%20along%20with%20the%20infusion%20of%20backward%20caste%20and%20Bahujan%20political%20rhetoric%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%2C%20looks%20to%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20self-avowed%20perception%20game%20as%20the%20party%20that%20best%20represents%20the%20backward%20castes.%20Chouhan%20is%20an%20OBC%2C%20while%20Modi%20has%20on%20several%20occasions%20referred%20to%20his%20caste%20identity%20to%20woo%20the%20sizeable%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20recent%20rally%20in%20Shahdol%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20described%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20national%20caste%20census%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9CX-ray%E2%80%9D%20that%20would%20determine%20the%20status%20of%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20tribal%20communities%20and%20determine%20how%20much%20representation%20they%20should%20be%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20speeches%20in%20MP%2C%20Modi%20sought%20to%20label%20the%20opposition%20as%20working%20against%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20nation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20On%20September%2014%2C%20amid%20a%20controversy%20over%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20Modi%20accused%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20running%20a%20hidden%20agenda%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdisintegrating%E2%80%9D%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%20On%20September%2025%2C%20the%20PM%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20outsourcing%20everything%2C%20from%20slogans%20to%20policies%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Csome%20Urban%20Naxals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5