this%20election%2C%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20and%20not%20the%20Congress%20that%20is%20grappling%20with%20internal%20strife%20and%20factionalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20feels%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20parties%20in%20the%2047%20seats%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20the%20end%2C%20as%20he%20feels%20the%20two%20parties%20are%20likely%20to%20retain%20their%20support%20base%20or%20numbers%20in%20the%20other%20regions.%20More%20than%2021%25%20of%20MP%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWill%20Kamal%20Nath%20finally%20end%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20long%20run%20in%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20states%3F%20More%20importantly%2C%20will%20he%20get%20a%20mandate%20strong%20enough%20to%20rule%20for%20the%20full%20term%3F%20These%20are%20questions%20that%20optimistic%20Congress%20supporters%20will%20be%20thinking%20about.%20For%20Chouhan%2C%20there%20is%20more%20at%20stake%20this%20time%2C%20primarily%20his%20political%20stature.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMishra%2C%20the%20Congress%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20media%20department%20chairman%2C%20says%20that%20this%20election%20season%2C%20there%20has%20hardly%20been%20any%20protest%20against%20the%20party%20by%20disgruntled%20workers%20or%20leaders.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20have%20been%20demonstrations%20and%20stone-pelting%20incidents%20outside%20the%20BJP%20office%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20first%20election%20where%20we%20have%20no%20dispute%20over%20the%20leadership%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20sure%20to%20have%20a%20big%20psychological%20impact%20on%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20image%20of%20the%20major%20players%2C%20especially%20Modi%2C%20when%20attention%20shifts%20to%20the%202024%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697596220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fw