-non-hindus-makes-tilak-aadhaar-a-must%2Farticleshow%2F104511472.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Violates%20Ceasefire%20In%20Jammu%2C%202%20Security%20Forces%20Personnel%20Injured%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Rangers%20violated%20the%20ceasefire%20along%20the%20Arnia%20sector%20of%20Jammu%2C%20in%20which%20two%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20jawans%20were%20injured%2C%20the%20BSF%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20major%20incident%20of%20ceasefire%20violation%20after%20the%20February%202021%20ceasefire%20understanding%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20army.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20men%20have%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20Government%20Medical%20College%20Hospital.%20The%20doctors%20said%20their%20condition%20is%20%26quot%3Bstable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%2017%20Oct%202023%20at%20about%202015%20hrs%2C%20the%20Pak%20Rangers%20resorted%20to%20unprovoked%20firing%20towards%20BSF%20troops%20which%20was%20befittingly%20retaliated%20by%20alert%20BSF%20troops%20in%20Arnia%20Sector.%20Two%20BSF%20personnel%20received%20bullet%20injuries%20who%20have%20been%20immediately%20provided%20medical%20assistance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BSF%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%2C%20the%20BSF%C2%A0on%20Tuesday%20arrested%20a%20Pakistani%20national%20who%20crossed%20the%20international%20border%20and%20entered%20Indian%20territory%20inadvertently%20in%20Punjab's%20Tarn%20Taran%20district%2C%20news%20agency%20ANI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20October%2017%2C%20forward%20deployed%C2%A0BSF%C2%A0troops%20apprehended%201%20Pakistan%20national%20ahead%20of%20the%20border%20fence%2C%20while%20he%20crossed%20the%20Indian%20border%20and%20entered%20Indian%20territory%2C%20in%20the%20area%20falling%20near%20the%20Village%20Khalra%20in%20Tarn%20Taran%20district%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official%C