ng%20against%20an%20enemy%20made%20of%20pure%20evil.%20If%20you%20stand%20for%20humanity%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20value%20of%20all%20human%20life%20%E2%80%93%20you%20stand%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised%20as%20the%20tensions%20in%20the%20region%20look%20to%20intensify%20further%20following%20the%20deadly%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20the%20Israeli%20Foreign%20Ministry%20said%20that%20an%20analysis%20of%20IDF%20operational%20systems%20indicates%20that%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20was%20fired%20by%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza%2C%20passing%20close%20to%20the%20Al%20Ahli%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20at%20the%20time%20it%20was%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntelligence%20from%20multiple%20sources%20we%20have%20in%20our%20hands%20indicate%20that%20Islamic%20Jihad%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20failed%20rocket%20launch%20which%20hit%20the%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMark%20Regev%2C%20a%20senior%20adviser%20to%20Netanyahu%2C%20backing%20his%20government's%20position%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20this%20tragedy%20in%20Gaza%2C%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20barrage%20against%20targets%20in%20central%20Israel.%20We%20had%20the%20siren%20here%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20a%20bomb%20shelter.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20they%20fired%20rockets%20at%20that%20same%20time.%20Hamas%20put%20out%20a%20statement%20that%20they%20were%20sending%20a%20long-range%20rocket%20on%20Haifa%20%5Bnorthern%20Israel%5D%20at%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Regev%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20no%20rocket%20actually%20reached%20Haifa.%20Where%20did%20that%20rocket%20go%3F%20Where%20did%20it%20land%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegev%20also%20noted%20that%20based%20on%20Israel's%20past%20conflicts%20with%20Gaza%20factions%2C%20it%20is%20known%20that%20about%2033%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20rockets%20fall%20short%20and%20land%20in%20