10859.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Xi%20Jinping%20Welcomes%20%26quot%3BDear%20Friend%26quot%3B%20Vladimir%20Putin%20For%20China%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20welcomed%20his%20%26quot%3Bdear%20friend%26quot%3B%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20to%20Beijing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20kicking%20off%20a%20multilateral%20summit%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%20Beijing%20this%20week%20hosts%20representatives%20of%20130%20countries%20for%20a%20forum%20on%20Xi's%20vast%20trade%20and%20infrastructure%20project%2C%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20top%20of%20the%20guest%20list%20is%20Putin%2C%20who%20is%20on%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20a%20major%20global%20power%20since%20Moscow's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20threw%20his%20regime%20into%20international%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20met%20Tuesday%20evening%20at%20an%20event%20kicking%20off%20the%20forum%2C%20video%20posted%20by%20Russia's%20foreign%20ministry%20showed%2C%20shaking%20hands%20and%20exchanging%20pleasantries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20took%20part%20in%20a%20group%20photo%20with%20other%20leaders%20attending%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20official%20banquet%2C%20Xi%20delivered%20a%20toast%20in%20which%20he%20alluded%20to%20recent%20geopolitical%20conflicts%2C%20but%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20historical%20(trend)%20of%20peace%26quot%3B%20was%20%26quot%3Bunstoppable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20the%20world%20today%20is%20not%20peaceful%2C%20downward%20pressure%20on%20the%20global%20economy%20is%20increasing%2C%20and%20global%20development%20faces%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20challenges%2C%20we%20firmly%20believe%20that%20the%20historical%20trends%20of%20peace%2C%20development%2C%20cooperation%2C%20and%20mutual%20wins%20are%20unstoppable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Xi%2C%20according%20to%20state%20news%20agency%20Xinhua.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPutin%20is%20due%20to%20hold%20in-depth%20talks%20with%20Xi%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20forum%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20said%2C%20with%20the%20war%20raging%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestinian%20militant%20organisation%20Hamas%20looming%20large%20over%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20talks%2C%20special%20attention%20will%20be%20paid%20to%20international%20and%20regional%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kremlin%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWestern%20countries%20led%20by%20the%20United%20States%20have%20rallied%20to%20Israel's%20side%20since%20October%207%2C%20when%20Hamas%20launched%20the%20deadliest%20attack%20in%20Israel's%20history%2C%20shooting%2C%20stabbing%20and%20burning%20to%20death%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20asked%20China%20to%20use%20its%20influence%20to%20help%20de-escalate%20the%20war%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20more%20than%20a%20million%20people%20in%20the%20blockaded%20Gaza%20Strip%20flee%20the%20relentless%20bombardment%20that%20Israel%20launched%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20brokered%20an%20entente%20between%20key%20Hamas%20backer%20Iran%20and%20its%20regional%20foe%20Saudi%20Arabia%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20and%20will%20send%20its%20Middle%20East%20envoy%20Zhai%20Jun%20to%20the%20volatile%20region%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20details%20have%20been%20given%20about%20where%20or%20when%20exactly%20Zhai%20would%20travel%2C%20though%20China's%20state%20broadcaster%20CCTV%20has%20said%20he%20will%20push%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20peace%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20maintained%20good%20relations%20with%20both%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20authorities%2C%20has%20called%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3