2C%20and%20views%20are%20up%2010x%20their%20usual%20rate.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMeta%20has%20removed%207x%20more%20content%20that%20is%20sympathetic%20to%20Hamas%2C%20but%20the%20groups'%20accounts%20are%20banned.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20small%20digital%20enclave%20they%20have%20left%2C%20the%20engagement%20on%20official%20Hamas%20social%20media%20accounts%20is%20booming%2C%20with%20followers%20skyrocketing%20and%20video%20views%20through%20the%20roof.%20On%20other%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20even%20without%20an%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhamas-committed-war-crimes-will-israels-government-do-the-same-2023-10%5C%22%3EHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20presence%20%E2%80%94%20sympathetic%20posts%20for%20the%20militant%20group%20are%20surging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas-affiliated%20accounts%20are%20largely%20banned%20across%20social%20media%20sites%2C%20including%20Meta's%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20group%20%E2%80%94%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20%E2%80%94%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20presence%20on%20the%20messaging%20platform%2C%20Telegram%2C%20where%20new%20followers%20are%20flocking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHamas'%20following%20on%20Telegram%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Telegram%20channel%20for%20Hamas'%20military%20wing%20has%20more%20than%20tripled%20its%20following%20in%20the%20days%20since%20the%20militant%20group%20began%20its%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20Israel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F16%2Ftech%2Fhamas-telegram%2F%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20analysis%20by%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20Digital%20Forensic%20Research%20Lab.%20Engagement%20on%20videos%20and%20other%20posts%20to%20the%20channel%20have%20similarly%20surged%2C%20receiving%20more%20than%2010%20times%20the%20usual%20number%20of%20views%2C%20per%20CNN.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Telegram%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20platform%20is%20evaluating%20how%20best%20to%20approach%20content%20moderation%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-posts-oversimplify-israel-hamas-war-2023-10%5C%22%3Emisinformation%20about%20the%20conflict%20surges%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20social%20media.%20Pavel%20Durov%2C%20Telegram's%20founder%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20October%2013%20that%20the%20platform's%20moderators%2C%20aided%20by%20AI%20tools%2C%20remove%20millions%20of%20posts%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bobviously%20harmful%26quot%3B%20each%20day%20but%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Btackling%20war-related%20coverage%20is%20seldom%20obvious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Hamas%20used%20Telegram%20to%20warn%20civilians%20in%20Ashkelon%20to%20leave%20the%20area%20ahead%20of%20their%20missile%20strikes.%20Would%20shutting%20down%20their%20channel%20help%20save%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20or%20would%20it%20endanger%20more%20lives%3F%26quot%3B%20Durov%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20destroy%20this%20source%20of%20information%2C%20doing%20so%20risks%20exacerbating%20an%20already%20dire%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETelegram's%20primary%20function%20is%20slightly%20different%20than%20other%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%20or%20X%20because%20Telegram%20requires%20users%20to%20seek%20out%20a%20specific%20channel%20to%20view%20its%20content%20instead%20of%20being%20shown%20suggestions%20promoted%20by%20an%20algorithm%2C%20Durov%20added%2C%20which%20he%20said%20makes%20the%20platform%20valuable%20for%20journalists%20and%20fact-checkers%20without%20significantly%20amplifying%20propaganda%20to%20unsuspecting%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOff%20Telegram%2C%20pro-Hamas%20posts%20surge%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20on%20platforms%20where%20Hamas%20doesn't%20have%20official%2