hases%20they%20otherwise%20would%20not%20make.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Insider%20found%20Chick-fil-A%20prices%20to%20be%20inflated%20compared%20to%20in-store%20prices.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652eb764211def8ed8374f4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Chick-fil-A%20sandwich%20cost%20less%20in-store%20compared%20to%20delivery%2C%20Insider%20found%20in%20a%20recent%20report.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInflating%20prices%20on%20delivery%20food%20has%20been%20around%20since%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20But%20lately%2C%20customers%20are%20noticing%20extreme%20price%20inflation%20%E2%80%93%20and%20they%20don't%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20report%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-delivery-apps-price-markups-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsider%20found%20prices%20for%20Chipotle%2C%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20and%20McDonald's%20were%2020%25%20to%2038%25%20higher%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20delivery%20orders%20made%20through%20apps%20like%20Uber%20Eats%20and%20DoorDash.%20Restaurant%20chains%20set%20menu%20prices%2C%20not%20delivery%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20Insider%20discovered%20that%20the%20chain%20was%20marking%20up%20the%20price%20of%20a%20traditional%20fried%20chicken%20sandwich%20on%20DoorDash%20by%20nearly%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarked-up%20menu%20prices%20are%20one%20of%20the%20top%20customer%20complaints%20DoorDash%20receives%2C%26quot%3B%20DoorDash%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20reason%20%E2%80%93%20among%20many%20%E2%80%93%20why%20DoorDash%20encourages%20restaurant%20partners%20to%20maintain%20delivery%20menu%20prices%20that%20more%20closely%20reflect%20in-store%20menu%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Chick-fil-A%20insider%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Got%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Anluna%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Enluna%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Or%20714-269-8873%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-settles-lawsuit-cash-gift-cards-report-says-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697575264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652eb1d5211def8ed8374343%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-settles-lawsuit-cash-gift-cards-report-says-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Six%20plaintiffs%20sued%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20chicken%20chain%20%26quot%3Bsecretly%26quot%3B%20inflated%20prices%20on%20delivery%20items%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20while%20promising%20low%20fees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nluna%40insider.com%20(Nancy%20Luna)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-settles-lawsuit-cash-gift-cards-report-says-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22200%20Killed%20In%20Airstrikes%20On%20Hospital%2C%20Says%20Gaza.%20Hamas%20Did%20It%2C%20Says%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20air%20strikes%20on%20a%20hospital%20compound%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20killed%20at%20least%20200%20people%2C%20officials%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20Palestinian%20territory%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20sparking%20widespread%20condemnation%20and%20fury.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Israel's%20army%20blamed%20a%20rocket%20misfired%20by%20militants%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAl%20Jazeera%20footage%20from%20the%20scene%20showed%20medics%20and%20civilians%20recovering%20bodies%20with%20white%20bags%20or%20blankets.%20Bloodstains%20and%20multiple%20torched%20cars%20were%20visible%20in%20the%20dark%20hospital%20courtyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20came%20just%20hours%20before%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20due%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20to%20balance%20US%20backing%20for%20Israel%20with%20stopping%20its%20war%20against%20Hamas%20from%20spiralling%20into%20wider%20regional%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20have%20been%20killed%20on%20both%20sides%20since%20Hamas's%20deadly%20October%207%20strike%20on%20Israel%2C%20with%20retaliatory%20air%20strikes%20and%20a%20siege%20of%20Gaza%20having%20a%20devastating%20impact%20on%20ordinary%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20escalation%20in%20tensions%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20Hamas-ruled%20Gaza%20said%20between%20200%20and%20300%20people%20displaced%20by%2010%20days%20of%20heavy%20bombardment%20were%20killed%20in%20%26quot%3Boccupation%20(Israeli)%20strikes%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Ahli%20Arab%20hospital%20in%20central%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHundreds%20of%20victims%20are%20still%20under%20the%20rubble%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bwar%20crime%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20prompting%20condemnation%20from%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHospitals%20and%20their%20grounds%20have%20been%20seen%20as%20safe%20havens%20for%20Gazans%20made%20homeless%20or%20displaced%20by%20the%20bombing%2C%20as%20they%20have%20been%20relatively%20spared%20from%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Jordanian%20capital%20Amman%2C%20dozens%20of%20protesters%20incensed%20by%20the%20strike%20in%20Gaza%20attempted%20to%20storm%20the%20Israeli%20embassy%2C%20an%20AFP%20correspondent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJordan%20was%20among%20Arab%20and%20Muslim%20states%20condemning%20the%20hospital%20strike%2C%20as%20did%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20agency%20supporting%20Palestinian%20refugees%20said%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20when%20one%20of%20its%20schools%20sheltering%20displaced%20families%20was%20hit%2C%20during%20Israeli%20air%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Hostages%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden's%20trip%20will%20come%2012%20days%20after%20the%20Palestinian%20militants%20of%20Hamas%20--%20under%20cover%20of%20a%20rocket%20barrage%20--%20burst%20through%20Israel's%20heavily%20fortified%20Gaza%20border%2C%20shooting%2C%20mutilating%20and%20burning%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShell-shocked%20Israel%20has%20responded%20with%20withering%20air%20strikes%20against%20targets%20in%20Gaza%2C%20leaving%20about%203%2C000%20Gazans%20dead%2C%20according%20to%20a%20toll%20from%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%20before%20the%20Ahli%20Arab%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20imposed%20a%20crippling%20siege%20on%20the%20impoverished%20territory%20and%20deployed%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20troops%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Gaza%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20full-scale%20ground%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20while%20also%20seeking%20to%20rescue%20the%20at%20least%20199%20hostages%20taken%20into%20Gaza%20by%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20released%20a%20video%20of%20one%20of%20the%20captives%2C%20French-Israeli%20woman%20Mia%20Shem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%2C%20Keren%20Shem%2C%20made%20an%20emotional%20plea%20for%20her%20safe%20return.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20begging%20the%20world%20to%20bring%20my%20baby%20back%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20a%20new%20conference%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20bids%20to%20free%20the%20hostages%20have%20gathered%20pace.%20Turkey%20said%20it%20was%20in%20talks%20with%20Hamas%20to%20secure%20their%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20were%20mixed%20views%20about%20how%20effective%20Biden%20could%20be%2C%20with%20some%20Palestinians%20blaming%20the%20United%20States%20for%20backing%20Israel%2C%20and%20even%20Israelis%20sceptical.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20believe%20anymore%20in%20politicians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Omer%20Nevo%2C%2023.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20trust%20anyone%20anymore%20after%20what%20has%20happened%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Iran%20warning%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraelis%20are%20still%20reeling%20from%20the%20worst%20attack%20in%20the%20country's%2075-year%20history%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20a%20mass%20mobilisation%20of%20reservists%20and%20the%20evacuation%20of%20residents%20from%20areas%20near%20Gaza%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20southern%20Israel%2C%20dozens%20of%20mourners%20gathered%20for%20the%20funeral%20of%20five%20members%20of%20the%20same%20family%20killed%20when%20militants%20attacked%20their%20kibbutz%20at%20Kfar%20Aza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20five%20coffins%20were%20draped%20in%20Israeli%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%2C%20back%20in%20Israel%20after%20a%20whistlestop%20regional%20tour%2C%20said%20Biden's%20visit%20would%20be%20a%20statement%20of%20%26quot%3Bsolidarity%20with%20Israel%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Bironclad%20commitment%20to%20its%20security%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupport%20also%20came%20from%20Germany%2C%20whose%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20was%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20must%20stand%20united%20behind%20Israel%20to%20defeat%20Hamas%2C%26quot%3B%20Israel's%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%2C%20alongside%20Scholz.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20already%20sent%20two%20aircraft%20carrier%20strike%20groups%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20%26quot%3Bto%20deter%20hostile%20actions%20against%20Israel%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20has%20put%202%2C000%20troops%20on%20deployment%20alert%20to%20be%20able%20%26quot%3Bto%20respond%20quickly%20to%20the%20evolving%20security%20environment%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%26quot%3B.%20US%20media%20said%20the%20troops%20would%20cover%20support%20roles%20such%20as%20medical%20assistance%20and%20handling%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20arch%20foe%20Iran%2C%20which%20backs%20both%20Hamas%20and%20Lebanon-based%20Hezbollah%20militants%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20warned%20against%20a%20Gaza%20invasion%20and%20Monday%20raised%20the%20spectre%20of%20a%20possible%20%26quot%3Bpre-emptive%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bby%20the%20resistance%20axis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran's%20supreme%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20said%20Tuesday%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20can%20stop%26quot%3B%20forces%20opposed%20to%20Israel%20if%20it%20keeps%20up%20its%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeadly%20flare-ups%20have%20rocked%20Israel's%20northern%20border%20with%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20army%20said%20Tuesday%20it%20had%20killed%20four%20militants%20attempting%20to%20infiltrate%20from%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20later%20said%20five%20of%20its%20fighters%20were%20killed%20%26quot%3Bperforming%20jihad%26quot%3B%2C%20taking%20the%20number%20of%20its%20fighters%20killed%20in%20the%20intensifying%20border%20skirmishes%20to%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20was%20asked%20on%20CNN%20whether%20US%20authorities%20had%20so%20far%20noticed%20Iran%20engaging%20in%20the%20conflict%20in%20new%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOutside%20of%20the%20rhetoric...%2C%20no%20we%20haven't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Corpses%20in%20the%20street'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20will%20also%20try%20to%20quietly%20steer%20Israeli's%20military%20response%2C%20as%20international%20alarm%20has%20grown%20about%20the%20devastating%20impact%20of%20the%20war%20on%20Palestinian%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEntire%20neighbourhoods%20have%20been%20razed%20and%20survivors%20are%20left%20with%20dwindling%20supplies%20of%20food%2C%20water%20and%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%20said%20hospitals%20were%20at%20breaking%20point%2C%20with%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20people%20taking%20shelter%20at%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20concerned%26quot%3B%20about%20disease%20outbreaks%20due%20to%20poor%20water%20supply%20and%20sanitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20corpses%20in%20the%20streets.%20Buildings%20are%20crashing%20down%20on%20their%20inhabitants%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jamil%20Abdullah%2C%20a%20Palestinian-Swede%2C%20hoping%20to%20flee%20the%20blockaded%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20smell%20of%20the%20dead%20is%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUNRWA%20says%20more%20than%20one%20million%20Palestinians%20--%20almost%20half%20of%20Gaza's%20population%20of%202.4%20million%20--%20have%20fled%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20UNRWA%20flour%20storage%20near%20Gaza%20City%20was%20hit%20by%20an%20Israeli%20strike%2C%20an%20AFP%20photographer%20said.%20Even%20as%20the%20smoke%20was%20still%20rising%20from%20the%20rubble%2C%20desperate%20residents%20collected%20flour%20from%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20dying%20of%20hunger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abu%20Hussni%20al-Hujein%2C%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20ordered%20residents%20of%20north%20Gaza%20to%20leave%20for%20the%20south%2C%20hoping%20to%20clear%20the%20area%20of%20civilians%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20ground%20assault%20that%20would%20involve%20gruelling%20urban%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20No%20escape%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEntire%20families%2C%20young%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%20have%20gathered%20belongings%20and%20fled%20to%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20bedding%20down%20in%20any%20available%20space%2C%20indoors%20and%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgypt%20kept%20closed%20Gaza's%20only%20border%20crossing%20not%20controlled