date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVasundhara%20versus%20Gehlot%20contest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20having%20a%20CM-face%20and%20pushing%20for%20collective%20leadership%20and%20projecting%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20lotus%20as%20the%20face%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20BJP%20central%20leadership%20has%20made%20its%20intention%20of%20a%20future%20where%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20is%20not%20central%20to%20the%20party%20in%20Rajasthan.%20There%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20Raje%20being%20asked%20to%20contest%20against%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20in%20Jodhpur%E2%80%99s%20Sardarpura%2C%20but%20reports%20also%20say%20she%20is%20clear%20that%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20CM%20candidate%20in%20return.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVasundhara%20Raje%20is%20currently%20an%20MLA%20from%20Jhalarapatan%20and%20has%20been%20for%20four%20consecutive%20tenues.%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20been%20the%20Sardarpura%20MLA%20since%201998.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697565465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17232338%2FF8kPaFzWgAA6sfg.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-rebellion-first-list-publicly-opposed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20loyalists%2C%20feeling%20sidelined%2C%20have%20threatened%20to%20fight%20as%20independents.%20Protests%20continue%20in%20several%20seats%20after%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20first%20list%20of%2041%20candidates%20was%20issued.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-rebellion-first-list-publicly-opposed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20foreign%20tourists%20killed%20in%20Uganda%20attack%20by%20suspected%20Islamist%20rebels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697565180000%2C%22visual%2