20probably%20lost%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20gold%20ring%20was%20found%20in%20a%20cracked%20condition%20and%20is%20pretty%20small%2C%20with%20a%20diameter%20of%20merely%209.4%20millimetres%2C%20and%20a%20width%20of%203.9%20millimetres.%20Ms%20Rogerson%20said%20that%20despite%20being%20so%20%26quot%3Btiny%20it%20only%20fits%20my%20little%20finger%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20was%20probably%20worn%20by%20a%20man.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20period%20rings%20were%20worn%20on%20all%20the%20joints%20of%20all%20the%20fingers%2C%20so%20it%20could%20have%20been%20worn%20on%20the%20upper%20joint%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcitibank-wins-case-after-firing-employee-for-lying-about-2-sandwich-lunch-expense-4490049%5C%22%3ECitibank%20Wins%20Case%20After%20Firing%20Employee%20For%20Lying%20About%202-Sandwich%20Lunch%20Expense%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERings%20engraved%20with%20French%20chivalric%20mottos%20were%20fashionable%20between%201400%20and%201500%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20It%20added%20that%20descriptions%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BI%20desire%20to%20serve%20you%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20to%20obey%20you%26quot%3B%20were%20often%20used%20by%20men%20wishing%20to%20serve%20their%20ladies%20as%20part%20of%20a%20courtly%20love%20tradition%20that%20swept%20across%20medieval%20Europe.%20The%20outlet%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20inscription%20is%20written%20in%20a%20type%20of%20French%20that%20was%20used%20in%20England%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Rogerson%2C%20anyone%20who%20could%20afford%20a%20fold%20ring%20at%20this%20time%20would%20have%20been%20among%20the%20elite%20who%20knew%20French.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ring%20and%20the%20silver%20tag%20were%20discovered%20by%20the%20same%20detectorist%2C%20although%20on%20two%20separate%20occasions.%20Ms%20Rogerson%20said%20as%20the%20ring%20was%20battered%20and%20cracked%20and%20the%20hooked%20tag%20damaged%2C%20it%20may%20have%20belonged%20to%20the%20same%20person%20who%20was%20taking%20them%20to%20be%20recycled%20at%20the%20time%20they%20were%20lost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tags%20were%20probably%20used%20in%20the%20Tudor%20era%20by%20women%20to%20hold%20up%20one%20layer%20of%20skirt%20from%20another%20so%20both%20can%20be%20seen%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697562900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ftnvgulg8_gold-ring_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-desire-to-love-you-engraved-medieval-ring-found-in-uk-by-metal-detectorist-4490658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20ordinary%20field%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20a%20metal%20detectorist%20made%20an%20exciting%20discovery%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20Middle%20Ages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-desire-to-love-you-engraved-medieval-ring-found-in-uk-by-metal-detectorist-4490658%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-desire-to-love-you-engraved-medieval-ring-found-in-uk-by-metal-detectorist-4490658%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-desire-to-love-you-engraved-medieval-ring-found-in-uk-by-metal-detectorist-4490658%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Releases%201%2C290-Point%20Manifesto%20For%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20released%20its%20Vachan%20Patra%20%E2%80%93%20the%20106-page%20manifesto%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%201%2C290%20promises%20of%20the%20party%20include%20filling%20up%202%20lakh%20vacant%20posts%2C%20creating%201%20lakh%20new%20posts%20in%20villages%20and%20turning%20the%20state%20into%20an%20industrial%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ET