member%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20did%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Gwalior%2C%20Scindia%20was%20present%20next%20to%20Gandhi%20throughout%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20elections%2C%20Scindia%20was%20the%20prime%20target%20of%20the%20BJP%20when%20they%20raised%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMaaf%20karo%20Maharaj%2C%20humara%20neta%20Shivraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Leave%20us%20alone%2C%20Maharaj%20(Scindia)%2C%20our%20leader%20is%20Shivraj)%E2%80%99%20while%20his%20speeches%20were%20the%20centre%20of%20attraction%20among%20the%20public.%20Poll%20results%20in%20Chambal%20reflected%20his%20popularity%20with%20the%20Congress%20winning%2026%20out%20of%2034%20seats.%20Out%20of%20all%20the%20six%20regions%2C%20Congress%20had%20performed%20the%20best%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20state%20Congress%20election%20campaign%20committee%20back%20then.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20a%20BJP%20MP%20and%20Union%20minister%20but%20does%20not%20hold%20any%20major%20responsibility%20for%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%2C%20despite%20the%20sorry%20state%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20region.%20Even%20the%20posters%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign%20carry%20a%20tiny%20photo%20of%20Scindia%20somewhere%20in%20the%20back%20though%20he%20appears%20prominently%20in%20the%20election%20campaign%20of%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20speculation%20has%20been%20rife%20about%20the%20decline%20in%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20stature%20in%20the%20BJP%20for%20some%20time.%20The%20rumours%20grew%20stronger%20after%20his%20loyalists%2C%20who%20had%20rallied%20behind%20him%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20started%20returning%20to%20the%20Congress%20one%20after%20the%20other%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%20Some%20prominent%20names%20among%20these%20are%20Baijnath%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Rakesh%20Gupta%2C%20Pramod%20Tandon%20and%20Samandar%20Singh%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151329%2F374191826_877937867035946_661087423820502970_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151329%2F374191826_877937867035946_661087423820502970_n.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151329%2F374191826_877937867035946_661087423820502970_n-300x200.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671841%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20leaders%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20(L)%2C%20J.P.%20Nadda%20(centre)%20and%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%E2%80%98reverse%20race%E2%80%99%20of%20Scindia%20loyalists%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERakesh%20Gupta%2C%20who%20was%20the%20working%20district%20president%20of%20Congress%20in%20Shivpuri%20district%2C%20had%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20with%20Scindia.%20Though%20the%20BJP%20had%20appointed%20him%20as%20the%20district%20vice%20president%2C%20he%20recently%20left%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20camp%20and%20returned%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CScindia%20had%20a%20different%20charm%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20was%20completely%20independent.%20At%20least%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20there%20was%20no%20leader%20who%20could%20control%20him.%20He%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98super%20power%E2%80%99.%20He%20also%20used%20to%20pay%20heed%20to%20party%20workers.%20But%20in%20the%20BJP%20there%20are%20many%20factions%20above%20him.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20is%20also%20there.%20There%20are%20several%20factions%20of%20the%20BJP%20within%20Chambal%20itself.%20He%20is%20facing%20difficulty%20in%20finding%20his%20foot%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20his%20concern.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20strike%20a%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20party%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Pohri%20tehsil%20in%20Shivpuri%20district%2C%20Arvind%20Dhakad%2C%20is%20also%20among%20the%20Scindia%20loyalists%20who%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20from%20Congress%20and%20has%20now%20done%20a%20%E2%80%98ghar%20wapsi%E2%80%99%20to%20Congress.%20He%20has%20claimed%20the%20ticket%20from%20Pohri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthree-madhya-pradesh-bjp-leaders-join-congress%5C%22%3EThree%20More%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20BJP%20Leaders%2C%20Including%20a%20Scindia%20Loyalist%2C%20Join%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20in%20Chambal%2C%20Congress%20was%20synonymous%20with%20the%20name%20of%20Scindia%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20many%20prominent%20leaders%20like%20Union%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20state%20home%20minister%20Narottam%20Mishra%2C%20and%20state%20president%20V.D.%20Sharma.%20Therefore%2C%20factionalism%20is%20natural.%20Besides%2C%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20clout%20has%20also%20reduced%20to%20half%20after%20switching%20parties%20because%20half%20of%20his%20supporters%20stayed%20behind%20in%20the%20Congress.%20Now%2C%20due%20to%20retrenchment%20among%20those%20accompanying%20him%2C%20he%20has%20become%20even%20weaker.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20does%20not%20enjoy%20the%20same%20authority%20in%20the%20BJP%20as%20he%20did%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20grievances%20of%20party%20workers%20were%20heard%20and%20resolved%20swiftly.%20But%20now%20there%20is%20no%20hearing.%20He%20paid%20heed%20only%20to%20those%20MLAs%20who%20were%20with%20him%20when%20he%20left%20the%20Congress%20and%20to%20those%20few%20who%20surrounded%20him.%20The%20rest%20of%20his%20supporters%20were%20completely%20ignored.%20The%20BJP%20did%20not%20accept%20us%20but%20he%20did%20nothing%20despite%20repeatedly%20being%20told%20about%20it.%20Those%20who%20rallied%20behind%20him%20are%20full%20of%20remorse%20now%20and%20will%20return.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20already%20returned%2C%20the%20rest%20will%20soon%20follow%20suit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20a%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Scindia%20loyalist%20who%20had%20chosen%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20Congress%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20coup%20in%20the%20state%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20people%20have%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20with%20%3Cem%3EMaharaj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20often%20talk%20to%20each%20other%20as%20our%20relations%20have%20hardly%20changed.%20They%20claim%20that%20%3Cem%3EMaharaj%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20not%20have%20the%20same%20status%20in%20the%20BJP%20as%20he%20had%20in%20the%20Congress%3B%20he%20has%20no%20monopoly%20in%20decision-making%20whereas%20during%20his%20time%20in%20Congress%2C%20he%20used%20to%20distribute%20tickets%20whether%20it%20was%20councillor%20or%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Gwalior-Chambal%2C%20Dev%20Shrimali%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CScindia%20was%20the%20balancing%20power%20within%20the%20Congress.%20Whether%20he%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20not%20he%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98super%20CM%E2%80%99%20of%20his%20area.%20Imagine%20if%2020-22%20MLAs%20could%20leave%20the%20party%20at%20his%20bidding%2C%20how%20many%20tickets%20would%20have%20been%20distributed%20at%20his%20behest%3F%20The%20Scindia%20family%20had%20a%20powerful%20place%20in%20Congress%20because%20they%20could%20topple%20the%20government%2C%20and%20they%20did.%20Now%2C%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20if%20he%20is%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20topple%20the%20government%2C%20he%20would%20lose%20his%20relevance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20when%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20own%20cut-outs%20are%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%2C%20it%20is%20but%20natural%20for%20his%20supporters%20to%20feel%20estranged.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20are%20gradually%20returning%20to%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20possible%20reason%20behind%20the%20decline%20in%20his%20influence%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20Chambal%20remained%20a%20stronghold%20for%20the%20Congress%20even%20after%20Scindia%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20It%20was%20perceived%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20departure%20that%20the%20party%20would%20face%20an%20existential%20crisis%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20close%20association%20with%20Scindia%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20about%2010-12%20years%2C%20but%20in%20vain%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Arvind%20Dhakad.%20%E2%80%9CActually%2C%20in%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20region%2C%20he%20was%20considered%20the%20sole%20leader%20in%20the%20Congress%20whose%20word%20was%20taken%20seriously.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20also%20had%20to%20join%20them.%20After%20he%20left%20the%20party%2C%20we%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20leader%20left%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20so%20we%20also%20followed%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Arvind%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20stayed%20strong%20in%20the%20region%20despite%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20departure%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20the%20latter%20was%20only%20%E2%80%9Cexploiting%20us%20for%20so%20many%20years%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20return%20of%20the%20Scindia%20loyalists%20to%20the%20Congress%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%20in%20various%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20morality%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20left%20the%20Scindia%20camp%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20Shivpuri%20district%20Congress%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20people%20went%20along%20Scindia%20because%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20and%20they%20wanted%20to%20milk%20the%20situation.%20Now%2C%20when%20they%20saw%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20declining%20stature%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20Congress%20forming%20the%20government%2C%20they%20have%20returned.%20If%20the%20BJP%20forms%20government%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20they%20repent%20and%20join%20hands%20with%20Scindia%20again%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17135255%2FF7vOUhSasAAXQ0V.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17135255%2FF7vOUhSasAAXQ0V.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17135255%2FF7vOUhSasAAXQ0V-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17135255%2FF7vOUhSasAAXQ0V-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680448%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20leader%20and%20Union%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Gwalior.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%20%40JM_Scindia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%20charge%20candidly%2C%20Rakesh%20Gupta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLeaders%20always%20have%20expectations.%20When%20big%20leaders%20can%20look%20after%20their%20own%20interests%20then%20what%20is%20the%20harm%20if%20small%20leaders%20like%20us%20look%20after%20our%20interests%3F%20Big%20leaders%20switch%20parties%2C%20once%2C%20twice%20and%20even%20four%20times%20depending%20on%20the%20situation.%20But%20we%20have%20only%20returned%20to%20our%20home%20(original%20party).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResentment%20among%20BJP%20cadre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20are%20deserting%20him%2C%20his%20presence%20in%20the%20party%20has%20left%20the%20BJP%20workers%20miffed.%20Some%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20various%20areas%20of%20the%20state%20left%20the%20party%20alleging%20that%20Scindia%20supporters%20are%20being%20given%20more%20importance%20in%20their%20respective%20assembly%20seats.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20leaders%20who%20were%20replaced%20by%20Scindia%20supporters%20in%20their%20assembly%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Joshi%2C%20who%20had%20been%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20state%20government%2C%20had%20lost%20the%20Hatpipliya%20seat%20to%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Manoj%20Choudhary%20in%202018.%20Later%2C%20Choudhary%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20party%20made%20him%20its%20candidate%20in%20the%20by-election.%20Former%20MLA%20Bhanwar%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20had%20also%20lost%20to%20Rajyavardhan%20Singh%20Dattigaon%20of%20Congress%20from%20Badnavar%20seat%20in%202018.%20Disappointed%20with%20his%20ticket%20cut%20from%20this%20seat%20after%20Dattigaon%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20Shekhawat%20left%20the%20party%20and%20joined%20Congress.%20Similarly%2C%20sitting%20Kolaras%20MLA%20Virendra%20Raghuvanshi%20was%20upset%20with%20Scindia%20supporter%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Yadav%20being%20given%20more%20preference%20in%20his%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjyotiraditya-scindia-bjp-narendra-modi%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20What%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20Said%20While%20Joining%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrabhuram%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20state%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20is%20an%20MLA%20from%20Sanchi%20assembly%20seat.%20Santosh%20Malviya%20was%20aspiring%20to%20contest%20elections%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20from%20here.%20But%20after%20the%20party%20gave%20preference%20to%20Scindia%20loyalist%2C%20Chaudhary%2C%20he%20got%20upset%20and%20left%20the%20party.%20One%20of%20his%20relatives%2C%20district%20panchayat%20member%20Preeti%20Malviya%20also%20bid%20adieu%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%20since%202013%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Malviya.%20%E2%80%9CI%20contested%20four%20elections%2C%20twice%20for%20councillor%20and%20twice%20for%20district%20panchayat%2C%20and%20won%20all%20of%20them.%20After%20Scindia%20and%20his%20men%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20original%20workers%20of%20the%20party%20were%20ignored.%20People%20who%20had%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20from%20Congress%20began%20dominating%20the%20Sanchi%20assembly%20constituency.%20When%20I%20felt%20I%20was%20being%20discriminated%20against%2C%20I%20left%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20also%20strongly%20believed%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20will%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Scindia%20factor%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20and%20Scindia%20will%20also%20be%20under%20pressure%20from%20his%20supporters%20for%20victory.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20can%20pressurise%20Scindia%20by%20insisting%20on%20how%20it%20sacrificed%20its%20own%20leaders%20and%20workers%20for%20his%20sake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConfusion%20in%20ticket%20distribution%20in%20the%20Scindia%20camp%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20looking%20at%20the%20list%20of%20tickets%20distributed%20by%20the%20BJP%20so%20far%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20party%20is%20perplexed%20about%20letting%20Scindia%20supporters%20contest%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Scindia%20left%20Congress%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202020%2C%2019%20of%20his%20supporter%20MLAs%20also%20rallied%20behind%20him.%20In%20the%20by-elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20gave%20tickets%20to%20all%2019%20Scindia%20supporters%20from%20their%20respective%20assembly%20seats.%20Of%20them%2C%2013%20won%20and%206%20lost.%20Out%20of%20these%2013%2C%20nine%20were%20also%20handed%20cabinet%20berths%20in%20the%20Shivraj%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20so%20far%20declared%20the%20names%20of%20its%20candidates%20in%20136%20out%20of%20230%20assembly%20seats%2C%20which%20includes%2011%20out%20of%2019%20assembly%20seats%20held%20by%20Scindia%20supporters.%20The%20BJP%20had%20won%20six%20out%20of%20these%2011%20seats%20in%20the%20by-elections.%20The%20party%20has%20handed%20tickets%20to%20Scindia%20supporters%20(including%20five%20ministers)%20in%20these%20six%20seats%20again%20but%20has%20cancelled%20the%20tickets%20of%20Scindia%20loyalists%20in%20three%20out%20of%20five%20seats%20on%20which%20it%20had%20earlier%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%20where%20the%20party%20has%20not%20yet%20declared%20candidates%20for%20Scindia%20supporters%2C%20there%20are%20seven%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Scindia%20camp%2C%20including%20four%20ministers.%20The%20party%20had%20declared%20the%20names%20of%20only%20the%20present%20ministers%20and%20MLAs%20in%20its%20fourth%20list%20excluding%20the%20names%20of%20these%20seven%20pro-Scindia%20MLAs%2Fministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20the%20initial%20three%20lists%20of%20candidates%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20announced%20its%20candidates%20for%20the%20lost%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20name%20of%20Scindia%20supporter%20Munnalal%20Goyal%20from%20the%20Gwalior%20East%20seat%20was%20not%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20out%20of%2019%20MLAs%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20following%20Scindia%2C%20only%20eight%20have%20got%20tickets%20till%20now%2C%20three%20have%20had%20their%20tickets%20cancelled%20while%20tickets%20for%20eight%20of%20them%20are%20pending.%20The%20only%20relief%20for%20Scindia%20is%20that%20his%20supporters%20have%20got%20tickets%20in%20two%20additional%20seats%20(Bhitarwar%20and%20Raghogarh).%20But%20so%20far%20only%2010%20of%20his%20supporters%20have%20been%20given%20tickets%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20tickets%20of%20some%20of%20the%20eight%20MLAs%20which%20are%20in%20limbo%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20current%20election%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98litmus%20test%E2%80%99%20for%20Scindia%2C%20journalist%20Shrimali%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHis%20base%20has%20weakened%20because%20a%20large%20number%20of%20leaders%20and%20voters%20having%20the%20Congress%20ideology%20have%20not%20drifted%20towards%20the%20BJP%20with%20him.%20He%20also%20lost%20the%20elections%20(Guna%20Lok%20Sabha)%2C%20due%20to%20which%20his%20influence%20as%20a%20celebrity%20also%20suffered%20a%20blow.%20This%20election%20is%20like%20a%20test%20for%20him%20to%20prove%20that%20he%20has%20managed%20to%20save%20his%20fort.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20several%20Congress%20district%20presidents%20in%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20region%20did%20not%20switch%20parties%20with%20Scindia%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20helped%20them%20climb%20the%20political%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CScindia%20is%20definitely%20a%20prominent%20leader%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20cadre-based%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Shrimali.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20respect%2C%20he%20will%20be%20counted%20only%20after%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20aware%20that%20he%20is%20sitting%20in%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20house.%20He%20had%20brought%20along%20his%20clan%20of%20supporters%20whose%20future%20revolves%20around%20him.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20parallel%20unit%20is%20running%20in%20the%20BJP.%20At%20present%2C%20he%20is%20in%20the%20good%20books%20of%20the%20party%20high%20command%20which%20is%20why%20he%20still%20commands%20some%20influence.%20Had%20it%20been%20somebody%20else%2C%20it%20would%20be%20worse.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJayant%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20who%20teaches%20journalism%20in%20Gwalior-Chambal%2C%20said%20that%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20is%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CScindia%20no%20longer%20has%20an%20aura%20in%20the%20BJP%20the%20way%20he%20did%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20observed.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20leaders%20and%20Scindia%20will%20have%20to%20adjust%20with%20them.%20The%20importance%20he%20gets%20depends%20on%20the%20will%20and%20grace%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership.%20And%20since%20there%20is%20a%20trend%20in%20the%20present%20BJP%20to%20use%20everyone%20as%20a%20pawn%2C%20Scindia%20is%20also%20a%20pawn%20who%20can%20be%20promoted%20at%20any%20time%20to%20bring%20down%20other%20leaders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F258848%2Fmp-polls-has-jyotiraditya-scindia-lost-significance-in-his-own-bastion-gwalior-chambal%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697542239000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17134810%2FF7wH24vbMAAIqma.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharaj-doesnt-have-power-in-the-bjp-scindias-clout-wanes-as-loyalists-return-to-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20his%20supporters%20who%20deserted%20him%20say%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20no%20longer%20command%20the%20kind%20of%20influence%20he%20had%20in%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20whilst%20he%20was%20in%20Congress.%20Some%20of%20his%20aides%2C%20now%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20are%20unhappy%20over%20being%20denied%20tickets%20for%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharaj-doesnt-have-power-in-the-bjp-scindias-clout-wanes-as-loyalists-return-to-congress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22P