%202020%2C%20a%20fall%20of%2075%25.%20The%20fall%20was%20sequential%3A%20going%20from%2055%20to%2042%2C%2045%2C%2023%2C%2021%20and%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDefence%20audit%20reports%20went%20from%20seven%20in%202017%20to%20zero%20in%202020.%20This%20was%20the%20same%20body%20that%20had%20done%20much%20to%20undo%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20through%20its%20several%20strong%20reports%2C%20including%20on%20the%202G%20auction%2C%20coal%20block%20auction%2C%20and%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20on%20this%20front%20in%20recent%20times%3F%20Where%20people%20inside%20it%20attempt%20to%20make%20it%20function%20independently%2C%20they%20are%20punished.%20A%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20parliament%2C%2012%20CAG%20reports%20were%20presented%20to%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20representatives.%20Days%20later%2C%20CAG%20officers%20who%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20audits%20that%20revealed%20corruption%20were%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20transferred%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fofficers-cag-reports-ayushman-bharat-bharatmala-transferred%5C%22%3EDattaprasad%20Suryakant%20Shirsat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20performance%20audit%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana.%20He%20had%20audited%20964%20hospitals%20in%20161%20districts%20of%20all%2028%20states%2C%20and%20found%20that%20in%202.25%20lakh%20cases%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Csurgery%E2%80%9D%20was%20shown%20to%20be%20later%20than%20the%20date%20of%20discharge.%20More%20than%201.79%20lakh%20such%20cases%20were%20found%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20for%20which%20the%20claimed%20amount%20was%20over%20Rs%20300%20crore.%20A%20web%20portal%2C%20which%20broke%20this%20story%2C%20reported%20that%20lakhs%20of%20claims%20continued%20to%20be%20made%20for%20people%20who%20were%20deceased.%20The%20audit%20also%20found%201.57%20lakh%20instances%20of%20duplicated%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%5C%22%3ETreatment%20for%20the%20Dead%2C%20Discharge%20Before%20Surgery%20and%20the%20Many%20Problems%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAtoorva%20Sinha%2C%20who%20had%20audited%20highway%20projects%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1057421%2Fcag-transfers-officers-involved-in-audit-reports-alleging-irregularities-in-central-schemes%5C%22%3Ewas%20transferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20his%20report%20found%20overrun%20costs%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20project.%20The%20report%20said%20a%20change%20to%20elevate%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20pushed-up%20costs%20to%20Rs%20250%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20as%20against%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%2018%20crore%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20tries%20to%20raise%20these%20issues%2C%20but%20is%20not%20able%20to%20get%20the%20government%20to%20accept%20any%20wrongdoing%2C%20much%20less%20to%20take%20action.%20The%20media%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20holding%20the%20government%20to%20account.%20It%20is%20the%20Opposition%20and%20civil%20society%20who%20are%20the%20primary%20targets%20of%20their%20coverage.%20Readers%20might%20be%20interested%20to%20know%20how%20the%20CAG%20was%20subverted%20from%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-controversial-record-of-a-modi-aide-who-may-head-the-enforcement-directorate%5C%22%3EGirish%20Murmu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Gujarat%20cadre%20officer%20who%20is%20so%20loyal%20to%20Mr%20Modi%20that%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20he%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.truthofgujarat.com%2Fgc-murmu-principal-secretary-narendra-modi-coaching-witnesses-subvert-truth%2F%5C%22%3Ecaught%20on%20tape%3C%2Fa%3E%20intimidating%20senior%20officials%20from%20testifying%20against%20his%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20DGP%20of%20Gujarat%20R.B.%20Sreekumar%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20State%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20from%20April%209%2C%202002%20to%20September%2017%2C%202002%2C%20in%20an%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20probing%20the%20Godhra%20riots%2C%20said%20that%20Mr%20Murmu%20%E2%80%9Ctutored%2C%20intimidated%2C%20forced%20and%20pressured%E2%80%9D%20him%20to%20depose%20in%20favour%20of%20Mr%20Modi.%20Mr%20Murmu%20was%20then%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sreekumar%20named%20another%20bureaucrat%20who%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%20and%20said%20he%20was%20told%20not%20to%20give%20his%20deposition%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20names%20would%20be%20opened%20up%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20summoning%20for%20cross-examination%E2%80%A6%20I%20was%20also%20threatened%20that%20if%20I%20gave%20a%20statement%20contrary%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20interests%2C%20I%20will%20be%20declared%20a%20hostile%20witness%20and%20dealt%20with%20suitably%20later.%20I%20told%20them%20that%20I%20would%20depose%20before%20the%20commission%20as%20per%20the%20statutory%20requirements%20and%20will%20not%20suppress%20the%20truth%2C%20because%20that%20would%20be%20an%20act%20of%20perjury%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Murmu%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cauthorised%20and%20entrusted%20with%20the%20task%20of%20tutoring%20and%20briefing%20government%20officials%20deposing%20before%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20by%20the%20highest%20authorities%20of%20the%20government%20and%20home%20department%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20a%20posture%20by%20Shri%20Murmu%20is%20possible%20only%20if%20he%20has%20the%20specific%20support%20and%20clearance%20from%20the%20higher%20authorities%20in%20the%20government%3A%20the%20hon%E2%80%99ble%20home%20minister%2Fthe%20hon%E2%80%99ble%20chief%20minister%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20made%20him%20the%20governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20then%20the%20CAG.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fpmindia.gov.in%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fpmindia.gov.in%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1697559938531000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3G8OPeI_Vrf2ug_i9JL1_z%5C%22%3Epmindia.gov.in%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20a%20section%20on%20transparency%20which%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20firmly%20believes%20that%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20are%20the%20two%20cornerstones%20of%20any%20pro-people%20government%E2%80%A6%20Transparency%20and%20accountability%20not%20only%20connect%20the%20people%20closer%20to%20the%20government%20but%20also%20make%20them%20an%20equal%20and%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20decision-making%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20hard%20to%20reconcile%20these%20words%20with%20the%20actual%20actions%20of%20Mr%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20on%20vital%20issues%20where%20opacity%20was%20preferred%20and%20promoted.%20This%20entire%20section%2C%20headlined%20%E2%80%9CQuest%20for%20transparency%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20site%2C%20has%20only%20184%20words%20and%20reads%20as%20if%20they%20were%20strung%20together%20by%20someone%20with%20little%20intellectual%20capacity%3A%20%E2%80%9CRules%20and%20policies%20were%20not%20framed%20in%20AC%20chambers%20but%20among%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDraft%20policies%20were%20put%20online%20for%20people%20to%20give%20their%20feedback%20and%20suggestions%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20is%20apparently%20an%20instance%20of%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20states%20that%20Mr%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20resolve%20to%20transparency%20backed%20by%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20put%20this%20commitment%20to%20practice%20indicates%20an%20era%20of%20open%2C%20transparent%20and%20people-centric%20government%20for%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%20No%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20The%20Narendra%20Modi%20years%20have%20been%20as%20opaque%2C%20and%20in%20many%20ways%20even%20more%20so%2C%20as%20those%20of%20any%20government%20before%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697534134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03200823%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-8.07.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftransparency-in-modi-era-cags-working-shows-it-remains-opaque%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20hard%20to%20reconcile%20these%20words%20with%20the%20actual%20actions%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20on%20vital%20issues%20where%20opacity%20was%20promoted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftransparency-in-modi-era-cags-working-shows-it-remains-opaque%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Israel-Palestine%20War%20Is%20a%20Stain%20on%20Every%20One%20of%20Us%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14144837%2FF8Ujv0qWkAA5W3q.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELondon%20Calling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0How%20does%20India%20look%20from%20afar%3F%20Looming%20world%20power%20or%20dysfunctional%20democracy%3F%20And%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Britain%2C%20and%20the%20West%2C%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20know%20about%20and%20perhaps%20learn%20from%3F%20This%20fortnightly%20column%20helps%20forge%20the%20connections%20so%20essential%20in%20our%20globalising%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20immense%20tragedy%20is%20playing%20out%20in%20Israel%20and%20Gaza.%20It%20has%20devoured%20thousands%20of%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20lives%2C%20mostly%20civilians%3B%20and%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20claim%20many%20thousands%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20staring%20at%20an%20unfolding%20catastrophe%20%E2%80%93%20and%20yet%20collectively%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20nothing%20to%20stop%20it.%20That%20is%20a%20stain%20on%20us%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20348px)%2085vw%2C%20348px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22348%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%20247w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%20526w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22422%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sophisticated%20military%20operation%20that%20Hamas%20launched%20earlier%20this%20month%20%E2%80%93%20firing%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20out%20of%20its%20Gaza%20stronghold%20north%20into%20Israel%20and%20sending%20thousands%20of%20its%20fighters%20over%20and%20under%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20heavily%20armoured%20border%20fence%20%E2%80%93%20had%20the%20advantage%20of%20surprise.%20For%20the%20Hamas%20fighters%2C%20this%20was%20largely%20a%20suicide%20mission.%20Their%20cruel%20goal%20was%20to%20take%20as%20many%20Israelis%20as%20they%20could%20down%20with%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20aimed%20at%20soft%20civilian%20targets%2C%20massacring%20scores%20of%20youngsters%20at%20a%20music%20festival%20and%20slaughtering%20families%20in%20kibbutz%20settlements%2C%20agrarian%20communes%2C%20within%20easy%20reach.%20If%20reports%20from%20the%20scene%20are%20to%20be%20believed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20I%20believe%20they%20are%20%E2%80%93%20the%20attackers%20on%20occasion%20tortured%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20their%20victims.%20More%20than%20a%20hundred%20Israelis%20were%20taken%20back%20to%20Gaza%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20depraved%20and%20despicable%20and%20was%20called%20out%20not%20only%20by%20a%20furious%20(and%20perhaps%20humiliated)%20Israeli%20government%20but%20also%20in%20Washington%2C%20London%2C%20Paris%20and%20Kyiv%2C%20by%20administrations%20which%20are%20allies%20of%20Israel%20and%20strong%20advocates%20of%20a%20rules-based%20international%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%2C%20which%20is%20both%20Islamist%20and%20nationalist%2C%20seems%20to%20want%20to%20goad%20Israel%20into%20a%20brutal%20response.%20It%20turned%20to%20terror%20to%20provoke%20another%20kind%20of%20terror%2C%20blanket%20air%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20and%20an%20Israeli%20ground%20invasion%20accompanied%20by%20a%20profound%20humanitarian%20tragedy.%20The%20strategic%20aims%20is%20to%20infuriate%20Arab%20opinion%20at%20the%20sight%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20agony%20so%20that%20the%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20which%20the%20US%20has%20been%20brokering%2C%20is%20derailed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%20may%20also%20believe%20that%20this%20initial%20conflagration%20will%20spark%20a%20wider%20regional%20war%20to%20achieve%20the%20armed%20movement%E2%80%99s%20stated%20goal%3A%20the%20eradication%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20fewer%20than%2020%20million%20Jews%20worldwide%2C%20of%20which%20about%20seven%20million%20live%20in%20Israel.%20They%20have%2C%20for%20centuries%2C%20faced%20poisonous%20antisemitism.%20Among%20the%20Israeli%20families%20struck%20in%20recent%20days%20are%20many%20which%2C%20two%20or%20three%20generations%20ago%2C%20suffered%20in%20the%20greatest%20infamy%20of%20the%20modern%20world%3A%20the%20Holocaust.%20About%206%20million%20European%20Jews%20were%20slaughtered%20in%20the%20industrial-scale%20genocide%20pursued%20by%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20Germany.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20couple%20of%20generations%20earlier%2C%20many%20of%20their%20forebears%20fled%20from%20the%20Russian%20Empire%20in%20the%20face%20of%20ferocious%20pogroms%2C%20officially-sanctioned%20rioting%20and%20attacks%20on%20Jews.%20In%20all%2C%20more%20than%202%20million%20near%20destitute%20Jews%20fled%20west%20in%20the%20thirty%20years%20before%201914%2C%20many%20making%20for%20America.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpalestine-solidarity-jantar-mantar-india%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98In%20Standing%20With%20Palestine%2C%20We%20Are%20Also%20Standing%20Up%20For%20Ourselves%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20killing%20of%20Israelis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0accompanied%20by%20the%20targeting%20of%20civilians%20including%20children%2C%20arouses%20the%20most%20terrible%20nightmares%20among%20so%20many%20Jewish%20households%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20state%20of%20Israel%20was%20set%20up%20in%201948%20because%20Jews%20were%20so%20evidently%20not%20safe%20in%20a%20state%20in%20which%20they%20were%20a%20minority.%20The%20answer%20was%20to%20have%20a%20homeland%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20of%20course%20an%20attempt%20to%20address%20one%20injustice%20created%20another.%20Palestinians%20regard%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20Israel%20was%20created%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Nakba%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20cataclysm%2C%20because%20it%20involved%20the%20displacement%20of%20most%20Palestinian%20Arabs.%20The%20Palestinians%20are%20now%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20dispersed%20and%20have%20no%20real%20state%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGaza%2C%20while%20nominally%20under%20Palestinian%20control%2C%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20Palestinian%20dispossession.%20In%20an%20area%20one-tenth%20the%20size%20of%20Goa%2C%20more%20than%202%20million%20people%20live%20without%20any%20real%20economic%20base.%20They%20are%20hemmed%20in%20on%20all%20sides.%20Only%20a%20tiny%20number%20are%20allowed%20through%20the%20Israeli%20border%20to%20work.%20To%20the%20south%2C%20the%20Egyptians%20are%20even%20more%20restrictive%20about%20who%20can%20use%20the%20Rafah%20crossing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%20continues%20to%20occupy%20Palestinian%20land%20captured%20during%20a%20war%20half-a-century%20ago.%20And%20in%20defiance%20of%20international%20law%2C%20it%20is%20encouraging%20Israelis%20to%20settle%20there%20in%20fortified%20communities.%20For%20Palestinians%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20they%20are%20being%20squeezed%20again%20and%20again%20%E2%80%93%20their%20land%20isn%E2%80%99t%20safe%2C%20their%20homes%20aren%E2%80%99t%20safe%2C%20their%20children%20aren%E2%80%99t%20safe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20Palestinians%20have%20not%20been%20well%20or%20wisely%20led.%20The%20Palestinian%20Authority%20which%20has%20some%20control%20over%20parts%20of%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank%20is%20a%20byword%20for%20corruption%20and%20nepotism.%20In%20the%20pressure%20cooker%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Hamas%20has%20channelled%20the%20anger%20of%20local%20Palestinians%20towards%20the%20pursuit%20of%20violence%20and%20terror%20rather%20than%20improving%20lives%20and%20building%20diplomatic%20alliances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%20is%20guaranteed%20the%20support%20of%20Iran%20and%20Syria%20however%20loathsome%20its%20acts.%20Israel%20knows%20that%20Washington%20will%20stand%20by%20it%20come%20what%20may.%20The%20United%20Nations%2C%20the%20one%20practical%20friend%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20through%20the%20decades%2C%20is%20able%20to%20do%20nothing%20but%20issue%20platitudes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20hardliners%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20profound%20suffering%20in%20their%20own%20community%20is%20seen%20as%20sufficient%20reason%20to%20inflict%20terrible%20suffering%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20moderate%2C%20consensus-minded%20voices%20%E2%80%93%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20%E2%80%93%20are%20once%20again%20being%20drowned%20out%20by%20the%20din%20of%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree-quarters%20of%20a%20century%20after%20Israel%20was%20created%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20a%20loop%20tape%20of%20hatred%2C%20distrust%2C%20destruction%20and%20barbarity.%20Those%20of%20us%20who%20look%20on%20in%20horror%20have%20no%20useful%20way%20to%20help%20achieve%20peace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAndrew%20Whitehead%20is%20an%20honorary%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nottingham%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20a%20former%20BBC%20India%20Correspondent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697533229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14144837%2FF8Ujv0qWkAA5W3q.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-israel-palestine-war-is-a-stain-on-every-one-of-us%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three-quarters%20of%20a%20century%20after%20Israel%20was%20created%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20a%20loop%20tape%20of%20hatred%2C%20distrust%2C%20destruction%20and%20barbarity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-israel-palestine-war-is-a-stain-on-every-one-of-us%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Parties'%20Leaders%20Meet%20Palestinian%20Ambassador%20in%20Delhi%20to%20Express%20Solidarity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17140704%2FF8jphGzXkAACKag.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20delega