mbassador%20know%20that%20there%20is%20also%20a%20different%20voice%20in%20India%E2%80%94the%20general%20voice%20of%20the%20people%20is%20for%20peace%2C%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20their%20homeland%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dipankar%20Bhattacharya%2C%20CPI%20(ML)%20general%20secretary%2C%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-leaders-meet-palestinian-envoy-express-solidarity-101697469898641.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20almost%20keeping%20quiet%20now%20and%20this%20amounts%20to%20endorsing%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20project%20of%20genocide%E2%80%94which%20is%20a%20huge%20departure%20in%20terms%20of%20foreign%20policy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MP%20Kunwar%20Danish%20Ali%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20post%20had%20sent%20a%20message%20that%20the%20entire%20India%20was%20with%20Israel.%20That%20created%20a%20confusion.%20The%20fact%20is%20India%20is%20standing%20with%20Palestine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Modi%20had%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20India%20is%20standing%20with%20Israel%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20since%20had%20to%20clarify%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20of%20supporting%20a%20sovereign%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697531899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17140704%2FF8jphGzXkAACKag.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-parties-leaders-meet-palestinian-ambassador-in-delhi-to-express-solidarity%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20also%20passed%20a%20resolution%20emphasising%20the%20international%20community's%20role%20in%20ensuring%20the%20rights%20and%20dignity%20of%20Palestinian%20people.%22%